<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
    	#set($commonUrl="https://f.51fanbei.com/h5")
		<title>邀请有奖</title>
	    <style type="text/css">
	    	.invitationGift_footer_wrap{
	    		position: fixed;
	    		left: 0;
	    		bottom: 0;
	    		width: 100%;
	    		background-color: rgba(0,0,0,.8);
                -webkit-box-sizing: border-box;
                box-sizing: border-box;
	    	}
	    	.invitationGift_footer{
	    		margin: 0.1rem;
	    	}
            .invitationGift_content{
                margin-top: 0.16rem;
            }
	    	.invitationGift_content img{
	    		width: 1.34rem;
	    		height: 1.34rem;
                border-radius: 0.08rem;
	    		margin-right: 0.2rem;
                float: left;
                -webkit-background-size: cover;
                background-size: cover;
	    	}
            .invitationGift_text{
                position: relative;
                float: left;
                width: 5.7rem;
                height: 1.34rem;
                color: #fff;
                font-size: 0.28rem;
            }
            .invitationGift_text p{
                position: absolute;
                top: 50%;
                left: 0;
                -webkit-transform: translateY(-50%);
                transform: translateY(-50%);
            }
            .invitationGift_text span{
                color: #FE963B;
            }
            .invitationGift_text p:nth-child(2){
                margin-top: -0.05rem;
            }
	    	.invitationGift_btn{
	    		width: 100%;
	    		height: 0.8rem;
	    		line-height: 0.8rem;
                text-align: center;
	    		margin-top: 0.16rem;
	    		font-size: 0.32rem;
                background-color: #FE963B;
                border-radius: 0.08rem;
                color: #fff;
	    	}
	    </style>
    </head>
    <body>
    	<input type="hidden" id="recommendCode" name="recommendCode" value="$!{recommendCode}">
    	<div class="invitationGift_wrap">
            <img src="$commonUrl/app/images/user/invitationGift1.png" align="absmiddle">
    		<div class="invitationGift_footer_wrap">
	    		<div class="invitationGift_footer">
	    			<div class="invitationGift_content clearfix">
##	    				<img src="$!{avatar}">
						#if($!{avatar}=='')
							<img src="$commonUrl/app/images/user/icon120.png">
						#else
							<img src="$!{avatar}">
						#end
                        <div class="invitationGift_text">
                            <p>亲，您的好友$!{userName}邀你来51返呗购物省钱，请注册的时候填写推荐人的<span>邀请码：$!{recommendCode}</span>，一起轻松开启省钱之旅吧～</p>
                        </div>
	    			</div>
	    			<div class="invitationGift_btn">马上注册拿返利</div>
	    		</div>
    		</div>
    	</div>
    	<script type="text/javascript">
    		var recommendCode = $("#recommendCode").val();
    		$(".invitationGift_btn").click(function(event) { // 马上去注册
    			window.location.href = "/app/user/register?recommendCode="+recommendCode;
    		});
    	</script>
    </body>
</html>
